snippet.title: Sword Art Online – Special Video
snippet.description:
Today is definitely a special day for Sword Art Online! 
With the end of the first part of Alicization and the announcement of the next game SWORD ART ONLINE Alicization Lycoris, we prepared a special video with a lot of news for you to discover what’s coming, enjoy!
